titleNullable: Real and Fake Face Detection - size 400x400
subtitleNullable: Research of changes in detection parameters
descriptionNullable:
The dataset is created from the dataset [Real and Fake Face Detection](https://www.kaggle.com/datasets/ciplab/real-and-fake-face-detection) by reducing the images from 600x600 to 400x400 as used in Kaggle and Twitter profiles. The ANTIALIAS filter from the Python library PIL was used.
